<div class="bg-white">
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex justify-between h-16">
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <%= link_to root_path do %>
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600">Anonymous Feedback</h1>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <%= link_to "Pricing", pricing_path, class: "text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-900" %>
          <%= link_to "About", about_path, class: "text-indigo-600 font-medium" %>
          <% if logged_in? %>
            <%= link_to "Dashboard", dashboard_path, class: "text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-900" %>
            <%= button_to "Logout", logout_path, method: :delete, class: "text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-900" %>
          <% else %>
            <%= link_to "Log In", login_path, class: "text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-900" %>
            <%= link_to "Get Started", signup_path, class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl">
        About Anonymous Feedback
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-indigo-100">
        Building a culture of honest, constructive feedback
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        We believe that honest feedback is essential for personal and professional growth. 
        But traditional feedback systems often fail because people fear retaliation or judgment.
      </p>
      <p>
        Anonymous Feedback solves this by creating a truly anonymous platform where team members 
        can give honest, constructive feedback without fear. Our multi-database architecture 
        ensures that feedback can never be traced back to individualsâ€”not even by us.
      </p>

      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p>
        Our platform uses a unique two-database architecture:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Identity Database:</strong> Stores user accounts and company information</li>
        <li><strong>Feedback Database:</strong> Stores all feedback responses</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        These databases are completely separate, with no foreign keys or direct links between them. 
        We use cryptographic hashing to ensure anonymity while still allowing you to view your 
        aggregated feedback once you've received at least 3 responses.
      </p>

      <h2>Privacy First</h2>
      <p>
        Privacy and anonymity are at the core of everything we do:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Multi-database architecture prevents tracing feedback to individuals</li>
        <li>Metadata (IP addresses, user agents) automatically deleted after 24 hours</li>
        <li>Minimum 3-response threshold before feedback is revealed</li>
        <li>No tracking, no analytics on feedback submitters</li>
        <li>Fuzzy timestamps ("a few days ago" instead of exact times)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Built for Teams</h2>
      <p>
        Whether you're a team of 5 or 500, Anonymous Feedback helps you:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Create a culture of continuous improvement</li>
        <li>Get honest insights about your performance</li>
        <li>Identify strengths and areas for growth</li>
        <li>Make feedback a regular part of your workflow</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        Have questions? Want to learn more? Reach out to us at:
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@anonymousfeedback.com">support@anonymousfeedback.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-white border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center text-gray-500">
        <p>&copy; <%= Time.current.year %> Anonymous Feedback. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</div>
